summary: An old standalone follower pack featuring 10 unique followers of each race.
descriptionHtml:
[center][size=3][color=#ffe599][b]
This mod is aimed at maintaining most of the aspects of vanilla races while also making them beautiful and strong.

Featured On[/b][/color][/size]
[url=http://www.skyrim-beautification-project.com/mods/mods/index.htm][img width=401,height=100]http://www.skyrim-beautification-project.com/gfx/skyrim-top-07.jpg[/img][/url][/center][line]
[center]Old Videos

[youtube]GOmCF8GT5E0[/youtube][youtube]eWTVdg-HtXg[/youtube][/center][center][color=#ffd966][size=4][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/55942/?tab=10&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodarticles%2F%3Fid%3D55942&pUp=1]----- Character Bio & Backstories -----[/url][/size][/color][/center]
[line]
[color=#ffa07a][size=4][font=trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif]About Mod[/font][/size][/color]

This follower pack contains 10 unique, standalone female followers of each race. All the followers are balanced for [i]Expert+[/i] level difficulty.
[line]
[color=#ffa07a][size=4][font=trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif]Features[/font][/size][/color]

[list][*][b]TBBP HDT bodies[/b] to get those things jiggling ![/*]
[*][b]HD tintmasks[/b] (makeup / warpaint).[/*]
[*]All followers are [b][i]essential[/i][/b] and [b][i]marriageable[/i][/b]. They will [b]auto level from 4-150[/b] and also has [i]Lightfoot[/i] perk so traps wont get triggered.[/*]
[*][b]Stealthy followers[/b] become [b]invisible[/b] when sneaking.[/*]
[*][b]Leveled vampire drain spells and damage boost[/b] for vampire followers.[/*]
[*][i]Common Files[/i] contains options for [b]Alternate Hair[/b], [b]No Warpaint[/b]. [i]Body Files[/i] contains option for [b]Wet Textures[/b].[/*]
[/list]
[line]
[color=#ffa07a][size=4][font=trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif]Summery[/font][/size][/color]

[center][u]Note : You can give Alayna, Dorcey and Nursha the same destruction spells and they will dual cast them.[/u][/center]

[line]
[color=#ffa07a][size=4][font=trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif]Installation[/font][/size][/color]

[b]For human followers :[/b]
1. Download and install [i]TPFollowers-Human Common Files[/i] from STEP-1 with any installer or manually.
2. Download and install one of the [i]TPFollowers-Human Body Files[/i] package from STEP-2 with any installer or manually.

[b]For elven followers :[/b]
1. Download and install [i]TPFollowers-Elven Common Files[/i] from STEP-1 with any installer or manually.
2. Download and install one of the [i]TPFollowers-Elven Body Files[/i] package from STEP-2 with any installer or manually.

[b]For beast followers :[/b]
1. Download and install [i]TPFollowers-Beast Common Files[/i] from STEP-1 with any installer or manually.
2. Download and install one of the [i]TPFollowers-Beast Body Files[/i] package from STEP-2 with any installer or manually.

[line]
[color=#ffa07a][size=4][font=trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif]Updating[/font][/size][/color]

[list=1]
[*]Dismiss all the followers from this mod in-game. If you are in a interior location then go outside. If you are in a exterior location then fast travel to somewhere else. Save your game. Quit the game.[/*]
[*]Download the updated files and overwrite with the existing files. Go in the game and check if its working properly.[/*]
[/list]
[line]
[color=#ffa07a][size=4][font=trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif]Uninstallation[/font][/size][/color]

[list=1]
[*]Dismiss all the followers from this mod in-game. If you are in a interior location then go outside. If you are in a exterior location then fast travel to somewhere else. Save your game. Quit the game.[/*]
[*]Deactivate [i]Common Files[/i] and [i]Body Files[/i] and delete them.
[/list]
[line]
[color=#ffa07a][size=4][font=trebuchet ms,helvetica,sans-serif]Compatibility[/font][/size][/color]

Compatible with [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/15524/?/]Amazing Follower Tweaks (AFT)[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/12933//?]Extensible Follower Framework (EFF)[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14037/?/]Ultimate Follower Overhaul (UFO)[/url], [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6554/?/]CBBE skin texture V2 V3 plus Thepal and UNP compatible by navetsea[/url].

Incompatible with Vampire Lord and Werewolf transformations for followers (they will become invisible after transforming).

files.name: 100 TPFollowers-Human Common Files
files.changelogHtml:
# Overall a nerf across all the followers reducing their magic damage and resistances as well as removing the other weapon perks to make them stick to their preferred weapon.

Alayna
- Removed Destruction perk Augmented Flames R2 (-25% fire damage)
- Removed 1H perks Bone Breaker R1, Bladesman R1.

Bianca
- Removed Alteration perks Magic Resistance R1, Magic Resistance R2 (-20% magic resistance).
- Removed Conjuration perk Twin Souls.

Mildred
- Removed Alteration perk Atronach (-30% magic absorb).
- Removed Destruction perks Augmented Flames/Frost/Shock R2 (-25% elemental damage on enchanted weapons)
- Removed 1H perks Hack and Slash R1, Bladesman R1.

Valora
- Removed 1H perks Bone Breaker R1, Bladesman R1.
- Removed 2H perks Deep Wounds R1, Skullcrusher R1
